members.name: fetchAllMembraneInvitations
members.description:
Fetches the membrane-invitations for all agents in the DHT

You can subscribe to `knowMembraneInvitations` to get updated with all the membrane-invitations when this call is done

Warning! Can be very slow

members.name: fetchAgentMembraneInvitation
members.description: Fetches the membrane-invitation for the given agent

members.name: fetchAgentsMembraneInvitations
members.description:
Fetches the membrane-invitations for the given agents in the DHT

You can subscribe to knowMembraneInvitations to get updated with all the membrane-invitations when this call is done

Use this over `fetchAgentMembraneInvitation` when fetching multiple membrane-invitations, as it will be more performant
